1
00:01:09,080 --> 00:01:09,840
Young lady.

2
00:01:10,000 --> 00:01:11,680
I see a dark shadow on your forehead.

3
00:01:11,680 --> 00:01:13,480
It is an omen of a great disaster.

4
00:01:13,560 --> 00:01:15,560
Today is not a good day for anything.

5
00:01:15,680 --> 00:01:17,440
If you dare speak such nonsense again,

6
00:01:17,440 --> 00:01:19,370
I'll give you a disaster right now.

7
00:01:26,400 --> 00:01:28,960
Boss Ji, I heard you know everything.

8
00:01:29,200 --> 00:01:31,200
What news are you looking for, Miss Song?

9
00:01:31,200 --> 00:01:34,330
I want the truth about the Song Army's military pay case,

10
00:01:34,400 --> 00:01:37,120
and the whereabouts of the Song Army's missing troops.

11
00:01:37,120 --> 00:01:38,400
I don't know about the second one.

12
00:01:38,400 --> 00:01:39,860
But as for the first one...

13
00:01:40,200 --> 00:01:41,330
What are your terms?

14
00:01:43,200 --> 00:01:44,080
Miss Song,

15
00:01:44,880 --> 00:01:46,320
this is a gambling house.

16
00:01:46,720 --> 00:01:48,680
As long as you win a bet against me,

17
00:01:49,120 --> 00:01:51,880
I will naturally give you the information you want.

18
00:01:51,880 --> 00:01:53,009
What are the stakes?

19
00:01:53,720 --> 00:01:56,320
Miss Song, why not take a look at the game first?

20
00:01:58,200 --> 00:02:01,040
This is the most dangerous game in our gambling house.

21
00:02:01,040 --> 00:02:04,160
You and I each need to choose an acquaintance,

22
00:02:04,160 --> 00:02:05,360
to stand on the stage.

23
00:02:06,080 --> 00:02:09,639
You just need to throw three knives while blindfolded.

24
00:02:10,400 --> 00:02:15,040
If you hit the apple on the person's head, you win.

25
00:02:15,440 --> 00:02:16,840
But if the person moves,

26
00:02:17,200 --> 00:02:19,720
or if you miss the apple on his head,

27
00:02:20,079 --> 00:02:21,200
you lose.

28
00:02:24,880 --> 00:02:25,480
Wait.

29
00:02:26,560 --> 00:02:27,200
Miss Song,

30
00:02:28,920 --> 00:02:30,650
I will also throw three knives.

31
00:02:31,240 --> 00:02:34,240
But my three knives will hit the person on the stage.

32
00:02:35,040 --> 00:02:36,970
Then you will have to make a choice.

33
00:02:37,440 --> 00:02:38,800
Do you save a life?

34
00:02:39,840 --> 00:02:40,970
Or do you win the bet?

35
00:02:43,440 --> 00:02:44,900
Are you scared, Miss Song?

36
00:02:45,040 --> 00:02:46,040
Too afraid to bet?

37
00:02:46,440 --> 00:02:47,440
What is the wager?

38
00:02:48,680 --> 00:02:50,680
I want the Bai Army's command token.

39
00:02:50,680 --> 00:02:54,040
Or Miss Song stays here to be my slave.

40
00:02:54,880 --> 00:02:56,360
Miss, let me do it.

41
00:02:57,560 --> 00:03:00,920
I should be the one participating in my wife's bet.

42
00:03:01,320 --> 00:03:02,480
If she loses,

43
00:03:02,880 --> 00:03:04,480
I will stay here as a servant.

44
00:03:04,840 --> 00:03:06,120
Bai Manchuan, you...

45
00:03:06,520 --> 00:03:09,520
Huanghuacai, if you want to bet, I'm with you.

46
00:03:09,720 --> 00:03:12,240
Lord Bai, are you serious?

47
00:03:13,720 --> 00:03:15,800
Huanghuacai, I believe in you.

48
00:03:16,480 --> 00:03:18,410
Lord Bai really is a devoted lover.

49
00:03:19,400 --> 00:03:20,280
In that case,

50
00:03:21,920 --> 00:03:22,920
let's begin.

51
00:03:34,120 --> 00:03:35,120
Miss Song.

52
00:03:36,480 --> 00:03:37,320
First knife.

53
00:03:45,600 --> 00:03:46,400
Second knife.

54
00:03:59,880 --> 00:04:00,720
Third knife.

55
00:04:03,200 --> 00:04:06,400
Huanghuacai, for the next knife, take two steps forward.

56
00:04:07,040 --> 00:04:08,520
Lower your left shoulder a bit.

57
00:04:08,520 --> 00:04:11,400
Angle your right hand slightly upward to the southeast.

58
00:04:11,400 --> 00:04:12,080
Trust me.

59
00:04:12,840 --> 00:04:15,880
Lord Bai, do you think I won't hurt you?

60
00:04:16,200 --> 00:04:17,399
I never said that.

61
00:04:18,000 --> 00:04:18,730
Third knife.

62
00:04:20,480 --> 00:04:21,880
Fly three inches higher!

63
00:04:28,200 --> 00:04:28,800
Manchuan!

64
00:04:29,200 --> 00:04:30,000
Bai Manchuan!

65
00:04:30,920 --> 00:04:31,650
Are you okay?

66
00:04:32,360 --> 00:04:33,240
I'm fine.

67
00:04:33,800 --> 00:04:35,730
What a pathetic pair of lovebirds.

68
00:04:36,840 --> 00:04:38,840
Boss Ji, you must accept your loss.

69
00:04:39,320 --> 00:04:40,920
It's time to tell us the news.

70
00:04:41,000 --> 00:04:41,880
Miss Song,

71
00:04:42,120 --> 00:04:45,780
I will send the information you want to the Zhongyi Marquis Manor.

72
00:04:51,560 --> 00:04:52,760
Cry out if it hurts.

73
00:04:53,200 --> 00:04:54,360
I won't laugh at you.

74
00:04:54,800 --> 00:04:56,730
You scream plenty usually anyway.

75
00:05:04,200 --> 00:05:05,730
Does your heart ache for me?

76
00:05:06,040 --> 00:05:07,840
I wish I were the one who got hurt.

77
00:05:14,680 --> 00:05:16,340
Then it's better that it's me.

78
00:05:16,480 --> 00:05:19,120
I'm just a useless fop anyway. I'm not important.

79
00:05:19,120 --> 00:05:20,920
No, you are very important.

80
00:05:21,400 --> 00:05:22,660
To whom am I important?

81
00:05:25,120 --> 00:05:27,840
Bai Manchuan, to me,

82
00:05:28,680 --> 00:05:30,140
you are like the Song Army.

83
00:05:39,560 --> 00:05:41,360
Huanghuacai, I'm sorry.

84
00:05:42,440 --> 00:05:44,100
Why apologize all of a sudden?

85
00:05:44,560 --> 00:05:46,960
It took me this long to realize my feelings.

86
00:05:48,040 --> 00:05:50,360
I'm also sorry for breaking your heart.

87
00:05:50,840 --> 00:05:51,640
It's okay.

88
00:05:52,440 --> 00:05:54,300
As long as you know you were wrong.

89
00:05:56,200 --> 00:05:57,860
I knew you were just stubborn.

90
00:05:58,360 --> 00:06:00,880
You can't hide your feelings for me.

91
00:06:03,640 --> 00:06:05,100
You're wounded right now.

92
00:06:05,560 --> 00:06:06,560
You can't do this.

93
00:06:10,200 --> 00:06:12,720
I'm tied to you for life anyway.

94
00:06:13,480 --> 00:06:14,880
You can't escape.

95
00:06:15,400 --> 00:06:16,800
We'll see how you behave.

96
00:06:20,440 --> 00:06:21,160
As you command,

97
00:06:21,160 --> 00:06:21,640
my wife.

98
00:06:25,720 --> 00:06:28,000
Miss, we're back.

99
00:06:29,080 --> 00:06:32,120
Lord Shen has been forming cliques for personal gain.

100
00:06:32,480 --> 00:06:35,940
Recently, he even tried to sideline the Third Prince in court.

101
00:06:36,200 --> 00:06:39,040
I knew my father wouldn't stay out of trouble.

102
00:06:40,040 --> 00:06:42,600
I heard you follow the Prairie Prince every day.

103
00:06:42,600 --> 00:06:43,600
Is there any news?

104
00:06:43,880 --> 00:06:46,040
The Prairie Prince's health is deteriorating.

105
00:06:46,040 --> 00:06:47,840
He hasn't left his tent for days.

106
00:06:48,120 --> 00:06:50,520
The tribal leaders are fighting fiercely.

107
00:06:50,520 --> 00:06:51,200
It's chaos.

108
00:06:52,520 --> 00:06:53,250
Total chaos.

109
00:06:55,680 --> 00:06:56,680
Chaos is good.

110
00:06:57,440 --> 00:06:58,440
Where is Manchuan?

111
00:06:58,440 --> 00:07:00,080
Lord Bai is injured.

112
00:07:02,840 --> 00:07:03,640
Who hurt him?

113
00:07:03,640 --> 00:07:04,600
It... it was...

114
00:07:04,600 --> 00:07:05,120
Ji Ruyu.

115
00:07:05,680 --> 00:07:06,640
Ji Ruyu?

116
00:07:08,200 --> 00:07:08,880
The reason?

117
00:07:09,120 --> 00:07:12,800
Lord Bai gambled his life for Miss Song.

118
00:07:15,720 --> 00:07:17,120
What's so good about her?

119
00:07:17,120 --> 00:07:19,050
That he'd risk everything for her?

120
00:07:20,720 --> 00:07:22,780
Didn't you say he still remembers me?

121
00:07:23,640 --> 00:07:25,300
Why does he still protect her?

122
00:07:25,680 --> 00:07:27,340
Protecting her with his life?

123
00:07:31,200 --> 00:07:33,480
Do you think I look like a madwoman right now?

124
00:07:33,480 --> 00:07:35,600
No, we wouldn't dare think that.

125
00:07:36,040 --> 00:07:37,240
Is what you said true?

126
00:07:37,360 --> 00:07:39,200
Lord Bai definitely has you in his heart.

127
00:07:39,200 --> 00:07:41,159
Otherwise, he wouldn't have asked to meet you the other day.

128
00:07:41,159 --> 00:07:41,920
Yes, yes, yes.

129
00:07:41,920 --> 00:07:44,240
It's all that Song Xuan's fault.

130
00:07:47,120 --> 00:07:47,720
Exactly.

131
00:07:49,040 --> 00:07:50,640
Manchuan has me in his heart.

132
00:07:50,720 --> 00:07:52,920
It must be Song Xuan standing in the way.

133
00:07:53,000 --> 00:07:54,000
You may leave now.

134
00:07:55,040 --> 00:07:56,240
I need to think.

135
00:07:56,960 --> 00:07:58,820
Think about how to kill Song Xuan.

136
00:08:06,800 --> 00:08:08,800
What sin did I commit in my past life,

137
00:08:08,880 --> 00:08:10,040
to meet this she-devil?

138
00:08:10,040 --> 00:08:11,560
We have to find a way to escape.

139
00:08:11,560 --> 00:08:13,160
Or she'll skin us alive sooner or later.

140
00:08:13,160 --> 00:08:14,480
Good heavens.

141
00:08:14,480 --> 00:08:15,560
You can't say that.

142
00:08:15,560 --> 00:08:16,440
If she hears this,

143
00:08:16,440 --> 00:08:17,520
we're both done for.

144
00:08:17,520 --> 00:08:18,580
Let's go, quickly.

145
00:08:29,880 --> 00:08:31,760
So you are the one behind Ji Ruyu.

146
00:08:32,200 --> 00:08:33,679
I'm here to honor the bet

147
00:08:33,679 --> 00:08:35,760
and tell Miss Song the truth.

148
00:08:38,120 --> 00:08:39,520
Where should I start?

149
00:08:40,120 --> 00:08:41,840
To Da Sheng, the Song Army

150
00:08:42,080 --> 00:08:43,880
is indeed a sharp blade.

151
00:08:44,520 --> 00:08:47,050
But if this blade isn't in the Emperor's hand,

152
00:08:47,080 --> 00:08:48,210
it becomes a threat.

153
00:08:48,880 --> 00:08:50,840
A subject whose merit overshadows the master

154
00:08:50,840 --> 00:08:52,680
usually has only one path.

155
00:08:54,680 --> 00:08:56,540
Miss Song should be able to guess.

156
00:08:56,720 --> 00:08:58,440
The Emperor didn't want the border army to be too powerful,

157
00:08:58,440 --> 00:09:01,200
so he tacitly allowed Lord Shen to strip their power,

158
00:09:01,200 --> 00:09:05,360
triggering a premeditated military and political massacre.

159
00:09:05,880 --> 00:09:06,720
Go on.

160
00:09:07,120 --> 00:09:08,780
The Emperor feigned concern,

161
00:09:08,920 --> 00:09:10,840
but turned a blind eye,

162
00:09:11,360 --> 00:09:14,200
tacitly allowing Lord Shen to embezzle 500,000 taels of military pay,

163
00:09:14,200 --> 00:09:16,680
causing the Song Army to run out of food on the front lines

164
00:09:16,680 --> 00:09:18,810
and be forced to fight the enemy alone.

165
00:09:19,480 --> 00:09:22,320
But the trapped Song Army remained unyielding,

166
00:09:23,040 --> 00:09:24,720
so they sent a small squad

167
00:09:25,400 --> 00:09:27,520
to seek reinforcements from the Imperial Court.

168
00:09:27,520 --> 00:09:28,780
What about that squad?

169
00:09:29,040 --> 00:09:31,120
If they were to show up alive now,

170
00:09:31,640 --> 00:09:34,120
wouldn't the embezzlement be exposed?

171
00:09:35,080 --> 00:09:38,120
So, that squad is already dead.

172
00:09:38,320 --> 00:09:39,780
Perhaps they aren't dead.

173
00:09:40,040 --> 00:09:42,520
After all, my men didn't find their bodies.

174
00:09:43,440 --> 00:09:45,900
But the chances of them being alive are slim.

175
00:09:47,200 --> 00:09:48,160
So, Miss Song,

176
00:09:48,880 --> 00:09:50,920
your father didn't die in battle.

177
00:09:51,320 --> 00:09:53,600
He was driven to his death by the Imperial Court.

178
00:09:53,600 --> 00:09:55,720
To cover up the flow of the embezzled funds,

179
00:09:55,720 --> 00:09:58,040
Shen Lingbo, the Second Miss of the Prime Minister's Manor,

180
00:09:58,040 --> 00:10:02,300
laundered the money in the name of the Marquis of Loyalty and Righteousness.

181
00:10:02,560 --> 00:10:03,720
She made the disappearance of those 500,000 taels

182
00:10:03,720 --> 00:10:06,440
look perfectly legal in the ledgers.

183
00:10:07,480 --> 00:10:08,810
I already know all this.

184
00:10:10,040 --> 00:10:12,900
That is exactly what makes Miss Shen so formidable.

185
00:10:13,720 --> 00:10:15,720
The Marquis of Loyalty and Righteousness was kind to you,

186
00:10:15,720 --> 00:10:18,080
so naturally, you wouldn't investigate your benefactor.

187
00:10:18,080 --> 00:10:19,680
Even if you noticed something wrong later

188
00:10:19,680 --> 00:10:21,480
and wanted to get to the bottom of it,

189
00:10:21,480 --> 00:10:24,080
you would inevitably implicate Bai Manchuan.

190
00:10:24,560 --> 00:10:25,560
What do you mean?

191
00:10:25,560 --> 00:10:26,560
What I mean is,

192
00:10:26,880 --> 00:10:29,000
as long as you are willing to cooperate with me,

193
00:10:29,000 --> 00:10:31,520
I can ensure the Song family's name is cleared,

194
00:10:31,520 --> 00:10:33,720
and ensure you slay your enemy with your own hands.

195
00:10:33,720 --> 00:10:34,560
You know that

196
00:10:34,880 --> 00:10:35,640
if I say it,

197
00:10:36,400 --> 00:10:37,160
I can do it.

198
00:10:37,720 --> 00:10:39,920
Miss Song, I remember telling you

199
00:10:40,600 --> 00:10:42,560
that there is no deep-seated hatred between us.

200
00:10:42,560 --> 00:10:44,420
Why don't we both get what we want?

201
00:10:44,880 --> 00:10:48,680
Besides, Miss Shen is far more complex than you think.

202
00:10:51,560 --> 00:10:52,480
I'll think about it.
